message.text:
「熊本の震災被害者のみなさまへ、マレーシアの子どもたちの“祈り”が届きますように！」
“日本語パートナーズ”としてマレーシアに赴任中の阿部宣行さんとマレーシアの中学生たち、先生たちによる熊本のみなさんへの祈りを込めたビデオレターと横断幕の活動が、マレーシアの邦字紙「南国新聞」で紹介されました。

message.text:
The Grand Opening Ceremony of the Japan Foundation Asia Center Phnom Penh Liaison Office was held on May 5, at the Embassy of Japan in Cambodia. 

The Ceremony was attended by H.E. Dr. Sok An, Deputy Prime Minster, Minister of the Office of the Council of Ministers, H.E. Dr. Hang Chuon Naron, Minister of Education, Youth and Sports, H.E. Mrs. Phourng Sackona, Minister of Culture and Fine Arts, H.E. Mr. Kumamaru Yuji, Ambassador of Japan and Mr. Tomoyuki Sakurai, Executive Vice President of the Japan Foundation Head Office as well as the honorary guests from the concerned Ministries and Institutions. 

For the remarks of the opening, please visit the Embassy’s HP at http://www.kh.emb-japan.go.jp/index-e.htm.
